comments: Sykes (IND) swipes down and makes contact with the ball then it makes contact with Igoudala's (GSW) lower body. The ball is last touched by Iguodala's before going out of bounds.
Toscano-Anderson (GSW) legally contests Sykes (IND) jump shot attempt.
Wiggins (GSW) does not extend his forearm into Sykes (IND) as he changes directions and comes to a stop.
Holiday (IND) and Wiggins' (GSW) mutually engage in marginal arm to arm contact and both players move around the off ball screen.
Craig (IND) jumps from point A to point B and delivers contact to Curry's (GSW) body that affects his driving shot attempt.
Iguodala (GSW) maintains a legal guarding position and he avoids making contact to Craig's (IND) arm during his jump shot attempt.
Holiday (IND) commits a take foul on Curry (GSW).
Jackson (IND) reaches in and makes marginal contact to Toscano-Anderson's (GSW) body at the start of the drive.

Brissett (IND) jumps vertically and he absorbs the oncoming body contact during Toscano-Anderson's (GSW) driving shot attempt. Craig (IND) briefly places his hand on Toscano-Anderson's back but he does not extend it.
Iguodala (GSW) makes marginal contact to Sykes' (IND) body that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Toscano-Anderson (GSW) slightly extends his hand into Brissett's (IND) front, but the contact is marginal and does not affect his ability to get to the rebound.
Curry (GSW) and Craig (IND) mutually engage in marginal contact as both players pursue the loose ball.
Sykes (IND) faces up and clamps Iguodala's (GSW) arm which affects his ability to move freely during the rebound.
Wiggins (GSW) commits a take foul on Sykes (IND).
Sykes (IND) commits a take foul on Curry (GSW).
Replay review of the out of bounds called against Brissett (IND) pursuant to a coach?s challenge was deemed successful. Thompson (GSW) touches the ball last before going out of bounds.
